                "text": "To compute the shipping cost for a 3 kg package shipped domestically, I will use the shipping-cost-skill formula:\n\n**Formula:**  \nShipping Cost = Base Rate + (Rate per kg × Weight in kg)\n\nFor domestic shipping, the typical values are:\n- Base Rate: $5\n- Rate per kg: $2\n\nNow, plug in the values:\nShipping Cost = $5 + ($2 × 3 kg)  \nShipping Cost = $5 + $6  \nShipping Cost = **$11**\n\n**The shipping cost for a 3 kg package shipped domestically is $11.**",
